<s> The Amaya team is proud to announce the Amaya 8.2+ Snapshot.  </s>
<s> Binaries (Linux, Windows NT/2000/XP), Debian and RPM packages are available at: This snapshot fixes a set of annoying bugs and includes new features.  </s>
<s> - Generation the date (on request) - New transformations: p to pre and pre to p . - New set of shortcuts: Ctrl t Ctrl ... for table editing Ctrl o Ctrl ... for forms Ctrl i Ctrl ... for information and style editing Ctrl m Ctrl ... for MathML Ctrl h Ctrl .. - A new table editor For more details see Irene.  </s>
