<s> Hi, First of all, thanks to the Amaya team for this new version.  </s>
<s> I just gave a try to the new snapshot, with a special focus on table stuff.  </s>
<s> 1) At first glance, I have noticed a weird bug.  </s>
<s> If I just create a new XHTML 1.1 document, add a table and give it a style="margin-left:20pt" and then a "width=100%", the bottom horizontal line of the border will extend far beyond to the right of the right border.  </s>
<s> The same defect shows in a printout of the document.  </s>
<s> I use the GTK binary version in Linux Redhat 8.0.  </s>
<s> It did not happen with GL version 8.2 on the same platform.  </s>
<s> 2) At start, I have been missing the "Enter key functionnality in tables but I must acknowledge that the new interface offers more possiblities.  </s>
<s> As matter of fact having *both features*, the "Enter" behaviour for the regular table stuff and the new menus for special things would be make me happy.  </s>
<s> 3) A more complicated document (I can send it off the list to anyone who is interested in) fails now to print.  </s>
<s> The generated PostScript is wrong at some point : an "ellipse" function (with a wrong number of arguments) is called for a list bullet for particular item when the "cer" function is called for all the other bullets !  </s>
<s> Anyway, I think the layout problem is the most serious issue.  </s>
<s> Thanks to the Amaya team for this new version.  </s>
<s> Best regards Serge Torres  </s>
